---
title: Pork & Oregano Sausages with Glazed Apples and Savoy Cabbage Mash
description: It’s bangers and mash, but as you’ve never seen them before…Tonight’s mash has been influenced by the classic English dish, bubble and squeak, named after the ‘bubbling’ and ‘squeaking’ sounds the cabbage makes as it cooks! Sharp and sweet all at once, the glazed apple sauce makes the perfect sauce sidekick to this warming and comforting dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-oregano-sausages-69a7fcf6-a37f7d46.jpg
